	<div class="module-feature-content">
					<h3 class="module-feature-title">
							<a href="http://www.barkerville.ca/activities/#placestoeat">
			
			Places to Eat
							</a>
						</h3>
		
		<p style="text-align: left;">Treasure seeking takes lots of energy. Good thing Barkerville&#8217;s bakery, restaurants, and saloon provide options for breakfast, lunch, dinner, and everything in between &#8211; from a quick coffee or ice cream cone to fully-licensed, multi-course meals. Dine in or take out at the world-famous Long Duck Tong Chinese Restaurant, experience the elegance of the 1860s in the Wake Up Jake Restaurant, the roar of the 1920s at the House Hotel Coffee Saloon, or find comfort in the 1930s charm of the Goldfield Bakery.</p>	</div>

	</div>
<!-- /module feature --><style>.themify_builder .feature-2-sub_row_9-0-1-0-0.module-feature { background-color: rgba(255,255,255, 0.53); padding-right: 4%; padding-left: 4%;  } 
.themify_builder .feature-2-sub_row_9-0-1-0-0.module-feature .feature-title {  } 
</style>

<!-- module text -->
<div id="text-2-sub_row_9-0-1-0-1" class="module module-text text-2-sub_row_9-0-1-0-1   ">
	
		
	
	</div>
<!-- /module text --><style>.themify_builder .text-2-sub_row_9-0-1-0-1.module-text {  } 
</style>

																																</div><div class="col3-1">																
																																
<!-- module feature -->
<div id="feature-2-sub_row_9-0-1-1-0" class="module module-feature feature-2-sub_row_9-0-1-1-0 no-chart layout-icon-top size-small  ">

	
	
	<figure class="module-feature-image">

					<a href="http://www.barkerville.ca/places-to-stay/">
		
					<div class="module-feature-chart" data-percent="0" data-color="rgba(222,93,93, 1)" data-trackcolor="rgba(0,0,0,0)" data-linecap="butt" data-scalelength="0" data-rotate="0" data-size="100" data-linewidth="2" data-animate="2000">
		
							<div class="module-feature-background" style="background: rgba(245,149,24, 1)"></div>				<i class="module-feature-icon fa fa-suitcase" style="color: rgba(0,0,0, 1.00)"></i>			
					</div><!-- .chart -->
		
					</a>
		
	</figure>

	<div class="module-feature-content">
					<h3 class="module-feature-title">
							<a href="http://www.barkerville.ca/places-to-stay/">
			
			Places to Stay
							</a>
						</h3>
		
		<p style="text-align: left;">It can take more than one day to explore everything Barkerville has to offer. That&#8217;s why we&#8217;re one of the few historic sites in Canada where guests can stay overnight, on-site! With 3 bed &amp; breakfasts and 3 large campgrounds, as well as additional hotels, motels, cabins and more in nearby Wells, on beautiful Bowron Lake, at Cottonwood House Historic Site, or the city of Quesnel&#8230; why not plan stay awhile for the ultimate Barkerville experience?</p>	</div>

	</div>
<!-- /module feature --><style>.themify_builder .feature-2-sub_row_9-0-1-1-0.module-feature { background-color: rgba(255,255,255, 0.58); padding-right: 4%; padding-bottom: 8%; padding-left: 4%;  } 
.themify_builder .feature-2-sub_row_9-0-1-1-0.module-feature .feature-title {  } 
</style>

																																</div><div class="col3-1 last">																
																																
<!-- module feature -->
<div id="feature-2-sub_row_9-0-1-2-0" class="module module-feature feature-2-sub_row_9-0-1-2-0 no-chart layout-icon-top size-small  ">

	
	
	<figure class="module-feature-image">

					<a href="http://www.barkerville.ca/activities/#placestoshop">
		
					<div class="module-feature-chart" data-percent="0" data-color="rgba(222,93,93, 1)" data-trackcolor="rgba(0,0,0,0)" data-linecap="butt" data-scalelength="0" data-rotate="0" data-size="100" data-linewidth="2" data-animate="2000">
		
							<div class="module-feature-background" style="background: rgba(245,239,61, 1)"></div>				<i class="module-feature-icon fa fa-gift" style="color: rgba(0,0,0, 1.00)"></i>			
					</div><!-- .chart -->
		
					</a>
		
	</figure>

	<div class="module-feature-content">
					<h3 class="module-feature-title">
							<a href="http://www.barkerville.ca/activities/#placestoshop">
			
			Places to Shop
							</a>
						</h3>
		
		<p style="text-align: left;">Sweet candy treats, presents from the past, exotic treasures, gold-nugget jewellery, hand-forged blacksmith items, old-fashioned photos, branded products and more &#8211; amidst the exhibits, interpreters, and architecture of BC&#8217;s gold rush history, there are plenty of opportunities to shop. Barkerville&#8217;s merchants combine authentic wares, gorgeous gifts, and one-of-a-kind souvenirs with a customer service experience you won&#8217;t find anywhere else.</p>	</div>

	</div>
<!-- /module feature --><style>.themify_builder .feature-2-sub_row_9-0-1-2-0.module-feature { background-color: rgba(255,255,255, 0.61); padding-right: 4%; padding-bottom: 8%; padding-left: 4%;  } 
