			Special Events
							</a>
						</h3>
		
		<p style="text-align: left;">It&#8217;s a season-long celebration with multiple special events throughout the summer! From our opening weekend Victoria Day Royal Tea to the fun and games of Dominion Day to the spectacular Chinese Mid-Autumn Moon Festival to our closing Murder Mystery weekend&#8230; there&#8217;s something for everyone!</p>	</div>

